name: Squirrel Necklace
description:
This tiny squirrel necklace was done by request, and I think he turned out pretty cute! This original squirrel was hand-carved, cast, and then molded. The squirrel pendant includes a fine 18 inches (46cm) sterling silver bead chain. Just a little something to wear everyday!

♥The size of the squirrel pendant is 1.5cm x 1.4cm. 

♥Sterling silver bead chain is 18 inches (46cm).

♥All metal used is sterling silver.

name: Autumn Necklace
description:
A gorgeous necklace, it comes with an oak leaf and acorn. They are hand-carved original pendants, that are so nice put together!It also has a cute name-Autumn! The Autumn range of jewelry includes the necklace and also an Autumn Ring.

♥Also available in Ring.

♥The size of the Oak Leaf pendant is 1.8cm and the Acorn is 1.5cm.

♥Sterling silver bead chain is 18 inches (46cm).

♥All metal is sterling silver.

name: Dove in Flight Necklace
description:
A sweet dove sterling silver pendant is attached to an 18 inches sterling silver bead chain. The dove is an original pendant carved and cast in 100% sterling silver. It is a nice gift for anyone who wants to spread the message of Peace!

♥The size of the dove pendant is 3.0cm x 1.9cm. 

♥Sterling silver bead chain is 18 inch (46cm).

♥All silver used is sterling silver.

name: Springtime Dove Necklace
description:
An exceptionally pretty piece of jewelry! The beautiful vintage style floret charms with a beautiful dove charm hand on a silver ring connector. The charms dangle on a fine 16'' sterling silver chain. Very feminine! This is an elegant statement necklace with a touch of vintage  glamour that will be ideal for any special occasion - or just whenever you want to feel utterly fantastic! 


♥Also available in Swarovski crystal gold and ruby colouring.

♥The size of the floret charms are 3.8cm x 1.7cm and dove is 1.8cm x 1.2cm.

♥Sterling silver chain is 16 inch (40cm).

♥All metal is sterling silver.

name: Love Birds Necklace
description:
Hand-carved charming dove on branch. It's an original pendant that's made of sterling silver with a fine 16 inches (40cm) sterling silver bead chain. On the side of the pendant is a purple flower and a green leaf Czech glass bead. So sweet and elegant at the same time, it is an exceptionally pretty piece of jewelry.

♥The size of the pendant is 6.0cm x 2.9cm.

♥The size of the Czech glass flower bead is 0.8cm x 0.7cm and the green leaf is 1.2 x 0.6cm.

♥Sterling silver chain is 16 inch (40cm)

♥All metal is sterling silver.
